<a href="/questions/149236-i-absolutely-loved-this-movie-and-didn-t">I absolutely loved this movie and didn&#39;t even know it was based on a book. Will the fact that I&#39;ve seen and loved the movie spoil the book for me? Is it worth checking out if already know the movie version of the story?</a>
