<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1322409-i-m-slightly-confused-by-the-ending-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm slightly confused by the ending. The bail bondsman tells Ree that she is entitled to most of the bond money and that the person who laid it down will not be coming back for it. Is the implication that Ree's father killed himself and left the money or was there another benefactor? I've reread the final exchange with the bondsman a few times but still can't make it out. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1322409'><a id="like_count_community_question_1322409" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1322409?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F112525.Winter_s_Bone">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1322409-i-m-slightly-confused-by-the-ending-the">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1322409-i-m-slightly-confused-by-the-ending-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
